parameters.name: PDSTIME
parameters.description:
Date/Time string of the form                   
                        yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sss such that the                                  
                        representation of the date and time for                                
                        Jan 01, 2000 00:00:00.000 would be:                                    
                        2000-01-01T00:00:00.000Z where Z indicates                             
                        Universal Time (also known as Zulu time).
